                    p
                      | When you first start playing Terrium, it feels a lot like Twisted Metal 4, except without all the different types of weapons.  We only have laser tag implemented for the beta.  However, there is an extra feature to the game that allows the player to create their own custom maps.  These maps can be shared across the world using my technology, the node game server.
                    p
                      img.img-fluid(src='img/Titus.png', alt='Node World UI')
                    h3 Object and Terrain Serialization
